oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Homecoming Float: "Sink the Lynx"
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Floats (Parades); Homecomings
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The student chapter of IEEE won first prize for their float for the Christian Brothers College homecoming in 1967. The game was played on Feburary 18 against the Lynx of Southwestern College. CBC won 60-58 after a last minute score by Ed Martin.
